Text: I went to hampi situated in Karnataka state of India where I meet with local
  fellows, talked about their culture & way of living as hampi is completely a village
  where there is a less electricity, local people are living with the expenses given
  by tourists as there n no. Of sights to explore ,so they have shared the lifestyle
  how they survived & live in a place where earning option is high only when you know
  something which tourists demands for
